%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Requestor / Project Manager
participant UI as Vendor Management UI
participant BFF as Vendor BFF
participant CACHE as Redis Cache
participant VMS as Vendor Management Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS Read schema"}

PM ->> UI: Click ON Request No.
UI ->> BFF: Get consolidated vendor result(requestId)

BFF ->> CACHE: Get consolidated result cache
alt Cache Hit
    CACHE -->> BFF: Cached consolidated matrix
else Cache Miss
    BFF ->> VMS: getConsolidatedResult(requestId)
    VMS ->> READDB: GET request header
    VMS ->> READDB: GET vendors, evaluators, submitted scores
    VMS ->> READDB: GET criteria weights and acceptance rules
    VMS ->> READDB: GET last 3 vendor avg scores
    VMS ->> VMS: Calculate weighted average per vendor
    VMS ->> VMS: Derive Accept / Reject result
    READDB -->> VMS: Result data
    VMS -->> BFF: Consolidated comparison matrix
    BFF ->> CACHE: Cache consolidated result
end

BFF -->> UI: Render vendor comparison, weighted score, result, past score